Advanced Routing with Omni-Channel Flows

Omni-Channel Flow brings all the functionality of Omni-Channel within Flow Builder. Use the power and flexibility of Flow Builder to define your routing rules and dynamically route work to the best agent.

Available in: Lightning Experience
Available in: Professional, Enterprise, Unlimited, and Developer Editions with the Service Cloud

How Does an Omni-Channel Flow Work?
When your customer initiates a chat, voice, or messaging conversation, launch an Omni-Channel flow to route the work item to a queue, skills, agent, or bot.

Create an Omni-Channel Flow
Create a flow from scratch. Or, get a headstart by creating one from an Omni-Channel flow template.

Assign an Omni-Channel Flow to a Chat Button
Route chats to the best agent dynamically using the Omni-Channel routing type and Omni-Channel flows.

Assign an Omni-Channel Flow to a Phone Channel
Route calls in a phone channel with an Omni-Channel flow, assigned to the channel for dynamic routing.

Assign an Omni-Channel Flow to Route Cases from Email-to-Case
Route cases from your customer support emails to qualified agents with an Omni-Channel flow.

Invoke an Omni-Channel Flow to Route Non-Real-Time Objects
Route non-real-time objects, such as cases, leads, and custom objects, with a defined routing logic in an Omni-Channel flow.

Manage Agents, Queues, and Skills with Omni Supervisor
Provide customer support for real-time channels with Omni-Channel rules.
Einstein Case Routing
Build AI solutions with Einstein for Service.
Track service metrics and manage your team.
Send surveys with Feedback Management.
title: Advanced Routing with Omni-Channel Flows
